caption: This is where all the hard work and magic takes place....this was the first golf course that I had ever stepped in at the age of 3.....this golf course means the world  to me...I actually never liked golf...but I started developing an interest in this game.....just love the environment and everything about this course......the trees the grass the birds...everything is special to me....when I was small I only used to go to the course to play in the sand (there are no strict rules in the Goa golf course + it is the only course in Goa) it was fun and today I thank everyone who has done so much hard work with me,for me....my caddy (there is no coach here) my mum!! I hope and pray that my most awaited dream comes true!!! Have a nice guys!!
